reviewText:
When I first bought this game, I didn't think I would enjoy it as much as I did.
The scenarios and everything else is hand painted, the game is an absolute work of art;
The bosses are gigantic compared to Jora, which makes it feel like a 2D Shadow of the Colossus and shows that you are indeed just a petty mortal trying to impress the gods;
Soundtrack is wonderful and goes very well with the setting of the game;
Combat is very difficult, can be both frustrating or rewarding, that is up to you (git gud).

11/10.   No cons to this game.

